  "title": "Scalp Protector Liquid",
  "body_html": "<p><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><span data-mce-fragment=\"1\">Specifically formulated to create a very thin, shine-free film that protects the scalp, preventing damage to the scalp during the application of hair adhesives and improving the adhesion of hair adhesives.</span></p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<h5 class=\"et_pb_toggle_title\">Advantages</h5>\n<div class=\"et_pb_toggle_content clearfix\">\n<p><img height=\"3\" width=\"44\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://luxhair.es/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/line_luxhair_2.png\" class=\"wp-image-145 alignnone size-full\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Protects the scalp, preventing irritation.</li>\n<li>Creates a very thin and undetectable protective film.</li>\n<li>Improves considerably the adhesion of tapes and liquid adhesives.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\u00a0<br></p>\n<h5 class=\"et_pb_toggle_title\">Format</h5>\n<div class=\"et_pb_toggle_content clearfix\">\n<p><img height=\"3\" width=\"44\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://luxhair.es/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/line_luxhair_2.png\" class=\"wp-image-145 alignnone size-full\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Each bottle, roll-on or spray, contains 50mL of product.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\u00a0<br></p>\n<h5 class=\"et_pb_toggle_title\">Recommendations for use</h5>\n<div class=\"et_pb_toggle_content clearfix\">\n<p><img height=\"3\" width=\"44\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://luxhair.es/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/line_luxhair_2.png\" class=\"wp-image-145 alignnone size-full\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Spread Scalp Protector with the cloth applicator on the areas of the scalp where the liquid adhesive or tape is to be applied later.</li>\n<li>After application, allow the liquid to dry until it is no longer sticky to the touch. A hairdryer can be used to speed up the drying process.</li>\n<li>For hygienic reasons, it is recommended that the use is personal so that the same applicator is not used for different hairpieces users.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<div class=\"et_pb_toggle et_pb_module et_pb_accordion_item et_pb_accordion_item_2 et_pb_toggle_close\"></div>\n<div class=\"et_pb_toggle et_pb_module et_pb_accordion_item et_pb_accordion_item_2 et_pb_toggle_close\"></div>\n<div class=\"et_pb_toggle et_pb_module et_pb_accordion_item et_pb_accordion_item_3 et_clickable et_pb_toggle_open\">\n<h5 class=\"et_pb_toggle_title\">Safety data sheet</h5>\n<div class=\"et_pb_toggle_content clearfix\">\n<p><img height=\"3\" width=\"44\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://luxhair.es/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/line_luxhair_2.png\" class=\"wp-image-145 alignnone size-full\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://luxhair.es/en/Product/scalp-protector-rollon#:~:text=Safety%20data%20sheet-,Link,-Related%20products\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Link</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<ul></ul>",
